-- Citi names Lawrence Ricciardi to board
-- 
-- Mon Jul 21, 2008 11:01am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/21/us-citigroup-ricciardi-idUSWNAB146620080721

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Citigroup ( C.N ) said on Monday it named Lawrence Ricciardi, former chief financial officer at International Business Machines Corp ( IBM.N ), to its board of directors. 

 Ricciardi bring the number of board members to 15, more than 70 percent of whom are independent. Ricciardi worked at IBM from 1989 from 1995, and held positions including general counsel and CFO. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)